Description: A perforated cylinder seal: of grey granite, the surface of which is rather damaged by chipping and wear. The remains of an incised inscription can be seen.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit III (Wiesbaden, 1964), pl. 115, abb. 649; P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit II (Wiesbaden, 1964), 1174.
Acquisition name: Purchased from: Rev George Denis Nash
